# Hello World!

And welcome to my blog.

Just wanted to get something up very quickly tonight after taking a break from working through the Rails Guide tutorial. I'm hoping to have much more content, including an intro to who I am, sometime this upcoming weekend.

Hopefully this pst works. I've been having a lot of trouble with Github lately. So consider this post just a test to make sure things are working correctly.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
